            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31568312">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">1. It is good to read one of the earliest work of political geography.
2. The &quot;pivot area&quot; happens to be quite similar in extent to &quot;high Asia&quot;, which is my research region, though I am concentrating at the physical geography part.
3. It will be interesting to see how the SCO or the Eurasian union might go in the future.</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-12 06:22</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                1. It is good to read one of the earliest work of political geography.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2. The &quot;pivot area&quot; happens to be quite similar in extent to &quot;high Asia&quot;, which is my research region, though I am concentrating at the physical geography part.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>3. It will be interesting to see how the SCO or the Eurasian union might go in the future.
