                  <span class="">1. It reminds me the &quot;history and philosophy of geography&quot; class during my first year of PHD.
2. Unfortunately looks like the question &quot;what is geography&quot; still do not have an answer most people agree on, though Mackinder and others have tried to give the definition and outline the scope of geography several times.
3. It is still hard to find a solid link between physical and...</span>
                <p class="pl">
